sentences: Roach made his record debut in 1960 with saxophonist Ike Quebec on the albums Heavy Soul and It Might as Well Be Spring and played with Willis Jackson.
He left the music business in 1970 and became involved in theater, playwriting and film.
Reportedly, he moved to California to the film industry, where he suffered a heart attack and died in 1980.
